1. sti enables interrupts after IDT setup
2. PIT fires IRQ0 after ~55ms (default 18.2 Hz)
3. PIC sends vector 8 to CPU (default mapping)
4. CPU invokes Double Fault handler NOT timer handler!
5. Double fault handler faults again inside itself
6. CPU cannot re-invoke #DF handler TRIPLE FAULT
7. Machine resets. Zero error message. Zero diagnostic.
